==Ancient Greek==

===Pronunciation===
*συνέδριον / sunedrion / soon-ed'-ree-on
*Neuter of a presumed derivative of a compound of [[σύν]]and the base of [[ἑδραῖος]]; a joint session, that is, (specifically) the Jewish Sanhedrim; by analogy a subordinate tribunal:

===Noun===
'''συνέδριον'''

# [[council]]

